                                LibraryAttribute defaultLibrary,
                                NamedObj containerModel,
                                javax.swing.JFrame sourceFrame,
                                SimpleSearchFrame simpleSearchFrame)
        Construct the GraphPatternSearchEditor.
        Parameters:
        entity - The model to put in this frame.
        tableau - The tableau responsible for this frame.
        defaultLibrary - An attribute specifying the default library to use if the model does not have a library.
        containerModel - The model that will import the searched results.
        sourceFrame - The frame that contains the model to import the searched results.
        simpleSearchFrame - The Simple Search Frame instance that opens this frame.

                         throws IllegalActionException,
                                NameDuplicationException,
                                MalformedStringException
        Fetch the search criteria of the graph pattern specified in this frame.
        Parameters:
        searchCriteria - The search criteria object to be set with the graph pattern criteria information.
        Throws:
        NameDuplicationException - Thrown if there are duplicated names of the attributes.

      • _close

        protected boolean _close()
        Close the pattern search window without asking anything.

        When the user is closing this window, it just hides for the simple search frame. So this does not require to ask whether the user wants to save or not.

        Overrides:
        _close in class GTFrame
        Returns:
